Michael Conner Humphreys https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Conner_Humphreys 0 Michael Conner Humphreys (born March 1, 1985) is an American actor best known for playing young Forrest Gump in the 1994 film of the same name, a performance for which he was nominated for a Young Artist Award.
